'''Futsal Klub Tirana''' or short '''KF Tirana''' ({{lang-en|Futsal club Tirana}}) is the most successful [[Albanians|Albanian]] [[futsal]] club. It won 5 out of 8 championships in the [[Albanian Futsal Premier League]]. It is the footsal wing of [[KF Tirana]].

